&lt;p&gt;Aviation emissions make up part of the general impact indicator ‘Total greenhouse gas emissions from transport’, and can be identified separately within that data set. A number of further metrics are published by the &lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.caa.co.uk"&gt;Civil Aviation Authority&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="reform-the-coastguard-and-search-and-rescue-capability"&gt;Reform the Coastguard and search and rescue capability&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is not practicable to measure the performance of this Structural Reform Priority until after the Coastguard has been reformed and the search and rescue capability is in place.&lt;/p&gt;

